TEFNUT · S250 · Patricia Inversion Node · S250 · S250: TEFNUT — THE INVERSE OF RIGHT-TO-REPRESENTATION

universe of origin : Heliopolis at the first sunrise and the deserts of Nubia in her exile — the lioness of moisture who, in her wrath, withdrew far from her father Ra and left the land parched and unheard until she could be coaxed home
seal               : The right to be spoken for is sacred precisely because the lioness can always walk away and leave the voiceless to the wilderness.
